name: The Wisdom of Fools - Graphic Novel + Extended Digital Edition
description:
'The Wisdom of Fools' is an 88-page graphic novel horror anthology from Fifth Dimension Comics. It's a full color book featuring 10 stories  and a pinup gallery by 15 writers and artists. 
The book is also numbered out of a strictly limited edition of 500. Once their gone, they are gone. 

If you missed the Kickstarter, here's your second chance!

Book comes signed by writer David M. Brown. 

Every purchase also includes the extended digital version (.pdf).
